  <p class="buy-card-notes"><strong>Why this pick:</strong> the highest-status SKU in the Hawaiian coffee category. When you give Private Reserve to a boss, client, or executive, the gift signals 'I know what good coffee is, and I picked the top of the line.' Classic Kona profile that almost no one dislikes.</p>
